Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:04.75,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as water flows without shape and wind blows without form,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.36,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}no case can stop you from deducing the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:08.36,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}People's feelings are the key to solving this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I want to find out how Ran really feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.32,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:47.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The old man only has 6 months left to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:51.86,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, that's what he thought he was hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.42,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But he was actually just being told to stay away from alcohol for 6 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:59.51,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The doctor, Yoshiteru Araide{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}, invited us to stay for dinner at his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:05.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But after a short blackout, Yoshiteru{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10} was found dead in the bathtub!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A doctor {\i1}and{\i0} a sports coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me, ask Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The team I'm coaching is at Teitan High School, the same school she goes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:36.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran went out to karate practice every evening to see {\i1}this{\i0} guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. You can check with the high school as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I go? I've got a burn to treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and you need to come to the clinic too, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use hiding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed you were limping just now,\Nlike something's wrong with your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What happened to your foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While I was coming downstairs in the dark, I stepped on something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I go help him treat everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a hold of the person that Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was talking to on the phone when the lights went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said that the time it took since Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told her the lights went out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to the time she reported that the lights went on was about a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to get Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to give her side of the story to ensure it matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I help treat everyone first, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, I can assist the doctor instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty good at stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, you can take over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her story matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time they weren't talking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was the six or seven seconds she took to answer the call waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was on the phone throughout the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, do you have a floor plan of this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the bathroom where your husband died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we must be here, right? This is the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the circuit breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You go left from the kitchen and turn left twice, then right once...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the maid, left the kitchen to check the breaker
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,around the time you told Masae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} about the blackout, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's odd that you were without light for a whole minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it'd take less than 30 seconds to get to the breaker from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has just started working here. She's not used to the house yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when your stepson saw that Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'d burnt her arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,didn't he say something like\N'You still put up with everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took care of Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} during his clinical training at Tohto Medical School.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her appendix almost burst because she ignored the pain for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that how Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} ended up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With my mother-in-law getting on in years,\NI can't take care of this household alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I hired her as a live-in maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing, really. Chiaki took care of the whole house by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s late mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She died four years ago from a car accident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems she was driving drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe it —\hshe'd always been a light drinker, since she knew she couldn't hold her alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's your mother-in-law's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You take the stairs to the left of the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the first large room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An old person like her living upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. She loves the view of the garden from that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the room next door,\Nso she could help if anything happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, the killer must've tried to call Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While she answered the call waiting,\Nthe killer slipped past the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,entered the bathroom,\Nand put the cord into the tub.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. How would she get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you whispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you have everybody do what they were doing during the blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, that's not a bad idea.\NWhile their memories are still fresh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're good with the bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew a boy who used to get injured all the time, so I got to be an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. The {\i1}nurse{\i0} shouldn't get injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's not serious. We can just wash it and put on a plaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, the Inspector's calling for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it. We'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you hand me a plaster from that cupboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Silly me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What am I thinking at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:03.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The breaker should be at the end of this hallway, to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:06.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful! This is where Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dropped the vase!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I helped her pick up the pieces.\NI felt so sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshiteru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} got really mad.\NHe even threatened to fire her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:33.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute. That could mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, are you all ready? Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger. We're ready at the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in place, in front of the breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, Takagi! Kill the breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, could you go to the breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,34 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, it took less than a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you cross this garden,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can get to the bathroom without sneaking past Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. There was enough time for her to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you cut it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't we told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everybody in this house had an alibi before the lights went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why keep bugging us about what happened during the blackout?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just had a terrible accident, and you're amusing yourselves with your ugly theories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have I done something wrong again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:53.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Their alibis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:10:01.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only one of those four people has a really solid alibi for the time of the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:07.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of the remaining three, one is very suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A fragment of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:15.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is this red mark blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:18.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what's this weird thing stuck to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's how it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:37.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means that there's only one person who could have been the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten seconds, round trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she did have the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the thing that we were concerned about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup. It's not even an issue...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't tell me, it's come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. A light bulb just went on in my head.\NI know the truth behind the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you could take me to the bathroom, I'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My back hurts a bit, so it'd help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? He wants to take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got wet in the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he wants to see if you can really get an electric shock by using that razor in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the Inspector and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The detectives said they\Nwere leaving for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! What a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Cause Uncle Kogorō said that once he gets out of the bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'll put on a deduction show for everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's figured out who the killer is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer? But didn't my husband die in an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he said he wants to have a bath and collect his thoughts first, so he might be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been 20 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s taking a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of that toothbrush moustache guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Another blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Could you go take a look at the breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why another blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, that man said he was running an experiment in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was fast. It's already back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that was {\i1}too{\i0} fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the killer, aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yōko Araide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yōko and the little boy have run off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me this was a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the killer? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just came to see if you were okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you were experimenting with the razor in the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted it to look that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but really, you wanted to kill me because I'd figured out the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then pretend to have discovered my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know I was talking on the phone throughout the blackout!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You created some kind of timer that could\Nshort-circuit the electricity in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used that penlight to make\Nyour way here in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then dropped the razor's extension cord into\Nthe tub where your husband was bathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, when someone reset the breaker, he'd die of an electric shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I was on the phone with my friend the whole time the lights were out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how could I come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was simple. Anybody could've done it with the phone's cordless handset and a mobile phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike the phone in the kitchen,\Nthe handset is cordless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Additionally, the main phone has\Na built-in rechargeable battery
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that makes it usable even during blackouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you switched receivers to the cordless handset and went to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used your mobile's speed dial to phone the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretending you had someone on call waiting,\Nyou stopped the conversation for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,grabbed the extension cord,\Nwhich you'd plugged in beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and snuck it into the tub while pointing the light at your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably told him to be careful to make him grab hold of a handrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you returned to the kitchen,\Nstill talking on the handset,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,switched back to the kitchen phone,\Nand waited for the lights to turn on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why when Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} reset the circuit, it tripped again immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the lights turned back on the first time, your husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who was holding the handrail,\Nwas electrocuted, and died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But anybody could've done that, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your plan was to create\Nan alibi using the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and also to establish alibis for the others\Nby blocking the corridor to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a problem arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took an extra\N30 seconds to reset the breaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,her alibi could not be established.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know why she took so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the {\i1}chawanmushi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the blackout,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} broke one of the {\i1}chawanmushi{\i0} dishes in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She held it under her arm and went upstairs to hide it in her room before going to reset the breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, your husband had threatened to fire her if she made another mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that burn on her arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what caused her burn and the mark on your mother-in-law's foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While leaving her room in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she stepped on a shard of the broken dish that Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dropped in the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:17:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s detour added\Nan extra 30 seconds to her trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and during that time,\Nthe old lady was still upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} couldn't have left the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since Ran was hanging on to him throughout the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now, Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only person who could have committed this crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me go, Inspector! Let me into the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's currently under investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}framed{\i0} her, and you call it an investigation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did she think we wouldn't notice the missing dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hadn't done anything,\Nyou would never have suspected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Even if she didn't hide the dish,\NI still would have figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hand you held the phone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left the kitchen, you were holding the phone in your left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was in your right hand\Nwhen the lights went back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It gave me the idea that you might've left the phone at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went to the bathroom with Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} when she discovered the body
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to make sure she wouldn't touch it and get a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Conan hadn't stopped Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nyou were going to stop him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiaki told me to take care of Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Four years ago, on the night Chiaki died, she called me and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Look after Tomoaki for me and make sure he doesn't turn out like my husband."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, I didn't know what she meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I understood after I married\Nhim and found Chiaki's diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I learnt that my husband was a womaniser\Nwho'd chase after any woman he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He{\i0} was the reason Chiaki began to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He drove her to her death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to advise you to turn yourself in as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, how kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I'm not doing this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this for Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got no idea, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may have been the one who set up the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} triggered it\Nby resetting the breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knowing that she {\i1}killed{\i0} a man\Nwill scar her for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the reason you didn't tell anybody the blackout was a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. So Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wouldn't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell the police that you killed your husband by putting him in the bathtub
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after drugging him and putting an electric cord connected to a timer in the tub
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:20:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to give him a fatal electric shock, then removing the timer during the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basically, tell them the murder occurred during the first blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, if you confess in court that I asked you to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then it'll get me and the Inspector into trouble too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose my human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for keeping you here so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:21:59.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:04.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell him I spoke too soon back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to help him if he ever needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:12.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know it's weird to ask you at a time like this, but if it's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...can I borrow that hand-knitted sweater you're wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:27.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}S-Sweater?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:29.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Kisaki Law Office"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, so this part is like this, and then this part...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, where'd you get that sweater?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I borrowed it off a friend.\NI just love the pattern!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's an Aran pattern. It's difficult, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that part's not quite right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, no! I'm going to knit this myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.81,0:22:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine. But don't come crying to me if you tangle it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I can't manage it, show me how to do it with another needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already knitted two sweaters for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you'd be better off giving a box of cakes rather than a sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been working hard lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sound jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, now how did this bit go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, those sweaters I knitted are in the way. Could you get rid of them for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No prob!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:26.82,Character Card,,0,0,0,,A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:23.75,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Hey, did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:26.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The doc sent it to me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:28.82,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And? Did you try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm wearing it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:35.73,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What're you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said what're you laughing about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:58.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:23:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?!
